ted\" data-text=\"Ὑγία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὑγία\"><span data-text=\"Ὑγία\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Ὑγία\">ΥΓΙΑ</span></span></span>·<span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΩΝ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span>]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"μηνῶν\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΩ[.</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Λοῦκις\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Λοῦκις\">ΛΟΥΚΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Κορνῆλις\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Κορνῆλις\">ΚΟΡΝΗΛΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Ὀνήσιμος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Ὀνήσιμος\">ΟΝΗΣΙΜΟΣ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"smaller\">vacat </span></em><span data-text=\"Ὑγία\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Ὑγία\">ΥΓΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΩΝ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span>]<span data-text=\"μηνῶν\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΩΝ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of IG</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Loukis Cornelis Onesimos. Hygia [--] years, [--] months [---].</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Kaibel proposes that the epitaph was originally for Cornelius, and that subsequently his wife(?) Hygeia was added to the burial, hence the space between the two.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Franz 1853 5407 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">38</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Lunate epsilon and sigma, uncial omega; use of interpuncts.</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
